    'en_US' => '<p>We recommend that research libraries list this magazine in their list of electronic journals. This publication system is also designed to be hosted and operated by research libraries as a support for the journal publication work of its associate faculty. For more information on how to use Open Journal Systems to manage and publish peer-reviewed journals, see the <a href="https://pkp.sfu.ca/">Public Knowledge Project</a>.</p>',
